headline: America Movil Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Up Y/Y
summary: AMX Q3 earnings soar, fueled by higher service and equipment revenues and strong regional growth.

headline: Is General Mills Now a Bargain After Dropping Nearly 30% in the Past Year?
summary: If you’re like a lot of investors weighing what to do with General Mills stock, you might be wondering whether these discounted prices are a threat or an opportunity. Over the past year, General Mills has dropped noticeably, with shares down nearly 30% over twelve months, and close to 25% lower since the start of the year. Even over a five-year stretch, the stock is down 7%. But don’t mistake red numbers for a lost cause. In fact, that steady decline has plenty of people asking if the market...
